---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Бесплатный генератор QR-кодов с цветами и логотипом" description="Бесплатный онлайн-генератор красивых QR-кодов: цвета, градиенты, стили точек и глазков, логотип в центре, рамки. URL, WiFi, текст, email, телефон. Скачайте PNG за секунды.">

    <section class="pt-24 pb-8 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-10 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <div class="inline-block bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm mb-6 border border-primary/20">
                100% бесплатно &middot; Без регистрации
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                Генератор <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-500 gradient-text">красивых QR-кодов</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-0 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Цвета, градиенты, стили точек, логотип в центре и рамки. Бесплатно и без регистрации.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
                    <!-- Type Tabs -->
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6" id="qr-tabs">
                        <button data-type="url" class="qr-tab active-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-link mr-1.5"></i>URL
                        </button>
                        <button data-type="wifi" class="qr-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-wifi mr-1.5"></i>WiFi
                        </button>
                        <button data-type="text" class="qr-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-font mr-1.5"></i>Текст
                        </button>
                        <button data-type="email" class="qr-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope mr-1.5"></i>Email
                        </button>
                        <button data-type="phone" class="qr-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-1.5"></i>Телефон
                        </button>
                        <button data-type="vcard" class="qr-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-id-card mr-1.5"></i>Контакт
                        </button>
                        <button data-type="sms" class="qr-tab px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold transition">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-sms mr-1.5"></i>SMS
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_360px] gap-8">
                        <!-- LEFT: Inputs + Styling -->
                        <div>
                            <!-- URL Form -->
                            <div id="form-url" class="qr-form">
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Адрес ссылки</label>
                                <input type="url" id="input-url" placeholder="https://example.com" class="qr-input" />
                                <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info text-primary/70 mr-1"></i>
                                    Этот код «зашьёт» ссылку навсегда — поменять её после печати нельзя.
                                    <a href="https://app.qrstars.ru/register" class="text-primary font-semibold hover:underline">Сделайте динамический QR бесплатно</a> — ссылку можно менять, видна статистика сканирований.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <!-- WiFi Form -->
                            <div id="form-wifi" class="qr-form hidden">
                                <div class="space-y-4">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Название сети (SSID)</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="input-wifi-ssid" placeholder="MyNetwork" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Пароль</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="input-wifi-pass" placeholder="••••••••" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Тип шифрования</label>
                                        <select id="input-wifi-enc" class="qr-input bg-white">
                                            <option value="WPA">WPA/WPA2</option>
                                            <option value="WEP">WEP</option>
                                            <option value="nopass">Без пароля</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Text Form -->
                            <div id="form-text" class="qr-form hidden">
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Произвольный текст</label>
                                <textarea id="input-text" rows="5" placeholder="Введите текст..." class="qr-input resize-none"></textarea>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Email Form -->
                            <div id="form-email" class="qr-form hidden">
                                <div class="space-y-4">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Email-адрес</label>
                                        <input type="email" id="input-email-addr" placeholder="hello@example.com" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Тема (необязательно)</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="input-email-subj" placeholder="Тема письма" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Сообщение (необязательно)</label>
                                        <textarea id="input-email-body" rows="3" placeholder="Текст письма..." class="qr-input resize-none"></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Phone Form -->
                            <div id="form-phone" class="qr-form hidden">
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Номер телефона</label>
                                <input type="tel" id="input-phone" placeholder="+7 (999) 123-45-67" class="qr-input" />
                            </div>

                            <!-- vCard Form -->
                            <div id="form-vcard" class="qr-form hidden">
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Имя</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="input-vcard-fname" placeholder="Иван" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Фамилия</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="input-vcard-lname" placeholder="Иванов" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Телефон</label>
                                        <input type="tel" id="input-vcard-phone" placeholder="+7 999 123-45-67" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Email</label>
                                        <input type="email" id="input-vcard-email" placeholder="ivan@mail.ru" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Организация</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="input-vcard-org" placeholder="ООО Ромашка" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Сайт</label>
                                        <input type="url" id="input-vcard-url" placeholder="https://example.com" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- SMS Form -->
                            <div id="form-sms" class="qr-form hidden">
                                <div class="space-y-4">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Номер получателя</label>
                                        <input type="tel" id="input-sms-phone" placeholder="+7 999 123-45-67" class="qr-input" />
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Текст сообщения</label>
                                        <textarea id="input-sms-body" rows="3" placeholder="Здравствуйте..." class="qr-input resize-none"></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Generate Button (mobile) -->
                            <button id="btn-generate-mobile" class="mt-6 w-full bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-base hover:bg-indigo-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 lg:hidden">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode"></i>
                                Сгенерировать QR-код
                            </button>

                            <!-- ─── Styling sections ─── -->
                            <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">

                                <!-- Dot style -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shapes mr-1.5 text-primary"></i>Стиль точек
                                    </label>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 sm:grid-cols-7 gap-2" id="style-picker">
                                        <button data-style="classic" class="style-btn active-style style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Квадраты</span></button>
                                        <button data-style="rounded" class="style-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Скруглённые</span></button>
                                        <button data-style="dots" class="style-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Точки</span></button>
                                        <button data-style="diamond" class="style-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Ромбы</span></button>
                                        <button data-style="star" class="style-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Звёзды</span></button>
                                        <button data-style="heart" class="style-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Сердца</span></button>
                                        <button data-style="cross" class="style-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="style-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Крестики</span></button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Eye (finder) style -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-eye mr-1.5 text-primary"></i>Стиль глазков
                                    </label>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-5 gap-2" id="eye-picker">
                                        <button data-eye="square" class="eye-btn active-eye style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="eye-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Квадрат</span></button>
                                        <button data-eye="rounded" class="eye-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="eye-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Скруглён.</span></button>
                                        <button data-eye="circle" class="eye-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="eye-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Круг</span></button>
                                        <button data-eye="leaf" class="eye-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="eye-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Лист</span></button>
                                        <button data-eye="dot" class="eye-btn style-thumb-btn"><canvas width="40" height="40" class="eye-canvas rounded"></canvas><span class="thumb-label">Точка</span></button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Color presets -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-palette mr-1.5 text-primary"></i>Цветовые пресеты
                                    </label>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-5 sm:grid-cols-10 gap-2" id="preset-picker"></div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Colors -->
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Цвет точек</label>
                                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <input type="color" id="input-fg" value="#1e293b" class="color-input" />
                                            <input type="text" id="input-fg-text" value="#1e293b" class="qr-input flex-1 font-mono text-sm" />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Цвет фона</label>
                                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <input type="color" id="input-bg" value="#ffffff" class="color-input" />
                                            <input type="text" id="input-bg-text" value="#ffffff" class="qr-input flex-1 font-mono text-sm" />
                                            <button id="btn-bg-transparent" type="button" class="px-3 py-2 text-xs rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 transition" title="Прозрачный фон"><i class="fa-solid fa-border-none"></i></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Gradient -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3 cursor-pointer">
                                        <input type="checkbox" id="input-gradient" class="w-4 h-4 accent-primary" />
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-fill-drip text-primary"></i>
                                        Градиент точек
                                    </label>
                                    <div id="gradient-controls" class="hidden grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 pl-6">
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Цвет 1</label>
                                            <input type="color" id="input-grad1" value="#4f46e5" class="color-input w-full" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Цвет 2</label>
                                            <input type="color" id="input-grad2" value="#a855f7" class="color-input w-full" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Тип</label>
                                            <select id="input-grad-type" class="qr-input bg-white text-sm">
                                                <option value="linear-tb">Линейный ↓</option>
                                                <option value="linear-lr">Линейный →</option>
                                                <option value="linear-diag">Диагональный</option>
                                                <option value="radial">Радиальный</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Eye color -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3 cursor-pointer">
                                        <input type="checkbox" id="input-eye-custom" class="w-4 h-4 accent-primary" />
                                        Отдельный цвет глазков
                                    </label>
                                    <div id="eye-color-controls" class="hidden flex items-center gap-2 pl-6">
                                        <input type="color" id="input-eye-color" value="#4f46e5" class="color-input" />
                                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">используется для трёх угловых маркеров</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Logo -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-image mr-1.5 text-primary"></i>Логотип в центре
                                    </label>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                                        <label class="cursor-pointer inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-300 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition">
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-upload"></i>
                                            <span id="logo-label">Загрузить изображение</span>
                                            <input type="file" id="input-logo" accept="image/*" class="hidden" />
                                        </label>
                                        <button id="btn-logo-clear" type="button" class="hidden px-3 py-2 text-xs rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white hover:bg-red-50 hover:text-red-600 hover:border-red-200 transition">Убрать</button>
                                        <label class="ml-auto flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 cursor-pointer">
                                            <input type="checkbox" id="input-watermark" checked class="w-4 h-4 accent-primary" />
                                            Подпись qrstars.ru
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Frame / caption -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3 cursor-pointer">
                                        <input type="checkbox" id="input-frame" class="w-4 h-4 accent-primary" />
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-vector-square text-primary"></i>
                                        Рамка с подписью
                                    </label>
                                    <div id="frame-controls" class="hidden grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 pl-6">
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Текст</label>
                                            <input type="text" id="input-frame-text" value="СКАНИРУЙ МЕНЯ" maxlength="32" class="qr-input text-sm" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Стиль</label>
                                            <select id="input-frame-style" class="qr-input bg-white text-sm">
                                                <option value="bottom">Подпись снизу</option>
                                                <option value="rounded">Скруглённая рамка</option>
                                                <option value="ribbon">Лента сверху</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Advanced -->
                                <details class="group">
                                    <summary class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 cursor-pointer select-none">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders text-primary"></i>
                                        Дополнительно
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down ml-auto text-xs text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition"></i>
                                    </summary>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3 pl-6">
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Уровень коррекции</label>
                                            <select id="input-ecc" class="qr-input bg-white text-sm">
                                                <option value="L">L (7%)</option>
                                                <option value="M">M (15%)</option>
                                                <option value="Q">Q (25%)</option>
                                                <option value="H" selected>H (30%)</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">Поля (отступ)</label>
                                            <input type="range" id="input-margin" min="0" max="6" value="2" class="w-full accent-primary" />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </details>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- RIGHT: Preview -->
                        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:self-start">
                            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center w-full aspect-square relative qr-preview-checker" id="qr-preview-wrapper">
                                <div id="qr-placeholder" class="text-center text-slate-400">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode text-5xl mb-3 opacity-30"></i>
                                    <p class="text-sm">Заполните поля и нажмите «Сгенерировать»</p>
                                </div>
                                <canvas id="qr-canvas" class="hidden max-w-full max-h-full"></canvas>
                            </div>
                            <button id="btn-generate" class="mt-4 w-full bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold text-base hover:bg-indigo-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hidden lg:flex">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode"></i>
                                Сгенерировать QR-код
                            </button>
                            <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                                <button id="btn-download-png" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm hover:bg-slate-800 transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" disabled>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i> PNG
                                </button>
                                <button id="btn-download-jpg" class="bg-white text-slate-900 border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm hover:bg-slate-100 transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" disabled>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i> JPG
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500 text-center">
                                Изменения в стиле применяются автоматически
                            </p>

                            <!-- Inline cross-sell to dynamic QR -->
                            <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 p-4">
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-primary"></i>
                                    Нужна статистика сканирований?
                                </p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                                    Сделайте динамический QR — ссылку можно менять без перепечатки, видны сканирования, гео и устройства. На тарифе FREE — бесплатно.
                                </p>
                                <a href="https://app.qrstars.ru/register" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-primary hover:underline">
                                    Создать динамический QR бесплатно
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-xs"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Static vs Dynamic comparison -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-3">Статический или динамический QR — что выбрать</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                Статический код «зашивает» данные в картинку навсегда. Динамический ведёт на короткую ссылку, которой управляете вы — её можно менять, видеть статистику и подключать сценарии. <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">У нас динамические QR доступны бесплатно</span> на тарифе FREE.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6">
                <!-- Static -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-4">
